movie_name: Mancunian Man: The Legendary Life of Cliff Twemlow
short_description: The life and obscure career of Cliff Twemlow, an actor, composer, screenwriter, and novelist from Manchester, who was a pioneer in the production of independently-made low-budget British action films made for the home video market.
